Text: "I got inspired because of an Indian hindi movie which was named as \"yeh jawani\
  \ hay dewani\"\n One day i asked my self,\"If he can do then why should i can !\"\
  \ On that moment i decided to start exploring my on country i have visited some\
  \ of the existing places in India such as,\"Ponmudi kanyakumari and more\" we all\
  \ can understand the limitations of an 19yrs old boy.\nI have decided that once\
  \ i complete my study's i have decided to go for a ride throughout all single part\
  \ of india to know more about the all the culture and traditions of my country"
